Others: Thomas Partey, Joseph Painstil, Kingsley Schindler, and Osman Ibrahim have withdrawn from the Black Stars vs Sudan game due to injuries.
The Black Stars are set to face Sudan on Thursday, October 10 and Tuesday, October 15, 2024 in two very important Africa Cup of Nations qualifiers.
Thomas Partey is experiencing medical issues and will undergo further tests in the coming days.
Joseph Paintsil has been scheduled for an MRI on Monday, 7th October due to hamstring pain.
Osman Ibrahim has been ruled out due to calf muscle pain and was substituted in the 65th minute of his last game.
Kingsley Schindler is unable to join the Black Stars due to a medical emergency.
